Download and upload manager for 1-click hosters
	
designed for automatic management of sites like:

 - http://rapidshare.com/
 - http://megaupload.com/
 - http://gigasize.com/
 - http://mediafire.com/
 - http://4shared.com/
 - http://sendspace.com/
 - http://zshare.net/
 - http://filefactory.com/
 - http://easy-share.com/
 - http://badongo.com/
 - http://depositfiles.com/
 - http://hotfile.com/
 - (...)

main features:

 - graphical user interface in gtk+.
 - easy to expand with plugins.
 - lightweight and fast.
 - management of waits between downloads.
 - captcha recognition where needed.
 - management of interchangeable links.